{"tid":2517678,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯球迷會開始學連登封殺cctvb做法","createTime":"2021-05-05T12:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T13:09:11.000Z","uid":193217,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"36c38109bb92374e524e9bd81f92d7a776f3eb2e","tid":2517678,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:52:38.000Z","msg":"親愛的商業夥伴，<br />\n<br />\n16年前，曼徹斯特聯隊毫無債務。如今，自從 Glazers 家族槓桿收購球會之後，球會負債8.4億英鎊，但是他們已經通過分紅以及售賣股份，搏取了15億英鎊。目前球會的淨債為4.55億英鎊，意味著自2005年至今，他們只償還了8500萬英鎊的債務資本。這期間，球會老闆根本沒有投入任何資金。<br />\n<br />\n身為 Glazers 家族的商業夥伴，你們是曼聯全球球迷合理的針對對象。因為你們每年總和的2790萬贊助費，並沒有花在球隊的投資，讓曼聯可以與現在最強的球隊對抗，並落在他們之後。這些錢也沒注入奧脫福或訓練設施的翻新，這些都是 Glazers 不在乎的，它們也因此陳舊不堪。<br />\n<br />\n你們給的贊助收入結果是用來償還債務與分紅。贊助 Glazers 不代表你們在贊助曼聯，你們和 Glazers 互相維持著寄生上流的關係。Glazers 吸著你們給的資金，而你們卻利用曼聯全球的商機，球迷則被債務拖累，處在無力的情況下。支持 Glazers 其實就像是在攻擊曼聯。<br />\n<br />\n就因為如此，曼聯球迷會抵制你們的商品，讓你們的品牌名譽掃地，也並且會支持你們的競爭對手，直到你們和 Glazers 家族停止商業合作。在被收購之後，曼聯球迷已經利用一切的渠道來改變現狀：從和平示威到球迷公開信，甚至也有球迷合資想把球會買下。但是 Glazers 家族無視這一切。儘管他們答應會與球迷「重建信任」，Joel Glazer 卻拒絕出席上週與球迷的對話論壇。我們無計可施，才必須選擇攻擊 Glazers 家族最依賴的商業收入以及品牌名譽。<br />\n<br />\n全世界的曼聯球迷充滿血性，但也非常地忠誠。如果贊助商意識到與 Glazers 這腐敗的管理合作會影響你們品牌的聲譽以及商業成功，並選擇離開，我們相信所有的曼聯球迷會在將來重新擁護這些品牌 &mdash;&mdash; 因為你們和我們站在同一陣線，維護我們球會的價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n但是直到那一天，如果你們繼續與 Glazers 同謀，你們也是攻擊曼聯球會以及謀殺英國足球的共犯。<br />\n<br />\n一分錢也不再給。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVNAwEM51mz3tvVxWhKiBwmpUBheMPFJvA1WMvN2sHWYD?filename=4GmZZTi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GmZZTi.jpg&h=45fabda9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n封殺贊助商<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗版式dislike同評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曼迷團結了<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rt.com/sport/522942-manchester-united-fan-boycott-glazers-sponsors/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rt.com%2Fsport%2F522942-manchester-united-fan-boycott-glazers-sponsors%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn4Bs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=4075ee5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rt.com/sport/522942-manchester-united-fan-boycott-glazers-sponsors/</a>"},{"pid":"23d755467974152d0c246afebe15aa992080f8d4","tid":2517678,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"連登領先世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f31bf7b60acff567bc568f72cd026ed207c6e6","tid":2517678,"uid":140835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"遲早週街都係曼聯贊助商<br />\n點解要罷？"},{"pid":"5632e1acafbd0149c6ca9d6c37e49c270935149a","tid":2517678,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-9544767/Man-Utd-fans-bombard-shirt-sponsors-TeamViewer-negative-reviews-protest-against-Glazers.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticle-9544767%2FMan-Utd-fans-bombard-shirt-sponsors-TeamViewer-negative-reviews-protest-against-Glazers.html&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn4Bs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=f9d28156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-9544767/Man-Utd-fans-bombard-shirt-sponsors-TeamViewer-negative-reviews-protest-against-Glazers.html</a><br />\nDon't line the pockets of the Glazers!': Manchester United fans bombard shirt sponsors TeamViewer with negative reviews on Trustpilot as they launch boycott campaign against the club's global partners in a bid to drive out their American owners<br />\n先搞teamviewer"},{"pid":"1d537c661d5ec9d553df9c52bdff63cb1315c329","tid":2517678,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfWtfevzzQCEyXnuoudZDULdpaMxBWFtjJ3VucNLkfos